<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 06:21:58 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>贸易商称，中国恒力利用额外进口配额从道达尔购买中东石油</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/chinas-hengli-uses-extra-import-quota-buy-mideast-oil-total-traders-say-2024-12-10/</link><description>六名知情交易员表示，中国私营炼油商恒力石化已抢购中东原油，其中大部分来自法国石油巨头TotalEnergies，此前这家法国巨头囤积了大量石油，且伊朗对中国的供应收紧。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 06:11:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/chinas-hengli-uses-extra-import-quota-buy-mideast-oil-total-traders-say-2024-12-10/</guid></item><item><title>阿萨德倒台暴露中国中东外交局限性</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/assads-fall-syria-exposes-limits-chinas-middle-east-diplomacy-2024-12-10/</link><description>就在一年多前，中国热烈欢迎巴沙尔·阿萨德和他的妻子对中国进行为期六天的访问，使这位叙利亚前领导人摆脱了自2011年内战爆发以来多年的国际孤立状态。 。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 05:55:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/assads-fall-syria-exposes-limits-chinas-middle-east-diplomacy-2024-12-10/</guid></item><item><title>习近平表示，中国对实现今年经济增长目标充满信心</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-has-full-confidence-achieving-this-years-growth-target-says-xi-2024-12-10/</link><description>中国国家主席习近平周二表示，中国对实现今年经济增长目标、继续发挥世界经济增长第一引擎作用充满信心。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 05:37:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-has-full-confidence-achieving-this-years-growth-target-says-xi-2024-12-10/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：中国政策讨论提振股市，但债券受阻</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-12-10/</link><description>汤姆·威斯布鲁克 (Tom Westbrook) 对欧洲和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 05:33:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-12-10/</guid></item><item><title>中国半程马拉松奖品为牛、野生鱼和鸡</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-half-marathon-offers-cow-wild-fish-chickens-prizes-2024-12-10/</link><description>中国东北吉林省的一场半程马拉松宣布了不同寻常的奖品选择，第一名冲线的选手赢得一头牛，其他参赛者获得野生鱼、鹅或公鸡，以吸引更多参与者并推广当地农产品。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 05:01:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-half-marathon-offers-cow-wild-fish-chickens-prizes-2024-12-10/</guid></item><item><title>焦点：电池制造商的帮助将维持锂供应过剩</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/lithium-supply-surplus-set-stay-with-battery-makers-help-2024-12-10/</link><description>以中国运营商为首的许多锂矿仍在维持电动汽车（EV）电池所需原材料的生产，无视价格疲软足以引发大规模减产的情况，这为电池制造商带来了福音。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 04:04:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/lithium-supply-surplus-set-stay-with-battery-makers-help-2024-12-10/</guid></item><item><title>查看特朗普关税前中国11月出口增长放缓</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/view-chinas-november-export-growth-slows-ahead-trump-tariffs-2024-12-10/</link><description>11月份中国出口增速较上月放缓，而进口则萎缩，这表明随着美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普即将重返白宫带来新的贸易风险，人们对这个世界第二大经济体感到担忧。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 03:44:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/view-chinas-november-export-growth-slows-ahead-trump-tariffs-2024-12-10/</guid></item><item><title>中国出口大幅放缓，进口在特朗普加征关税前萎缩</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-export-growth-slows-imports-shrink-ahead-trump-tariffs-2024-12-10/</link><description>中国11月出口增速较前一个月放缓，而进口意外萎缩，这对世界第二大经济体来说是一个令人担忧的迹象，因为唐纳德·特朗普即将重返白宫带来新的贸易风险。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 03:38:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-export-growth-slows-imports-shrink-ahead-trump-tariffs-2024-12-10/</guid></item><item><title>中国承诺实施更多刺激措施，金价扩大涨势</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/gold-extends-gain-chinas-vow-policy-stimulus-2024-12-10/</link><description>周二金价延续涨势，主要消费国中国承诺加大政策刺激力度以帮助刺激经济增长，投资者等待美国通胀数据以进一步了解美联储的利率前景。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 03:27:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/gold-extends-gain-chinas-vow-policy-stimulus-2024-12-10/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾将继续在南海执行补给任务 不会导致局势升级</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-continue-resupply-missions-schina-sea-wont-escalate-situation-2024-12-10/</link><description>菲律宾总统小费迪南德·马科斯周二表示，尽管最近发生了与中国船只发生的事件，但该国将继续在南海执行补给任务，而无需部署海军。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 03:01:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-continue-resupply-missions-schina-sea-wont-escalate-situation-2024-12-10/</guid></item><item><title>台湾称，中国向该地区派遣了数十年来最大规模的海军舰队，威胁程度严重</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-reports-surge-chinese-military-aircraft-ships-operating-nearby-2024-12-10/</link><description>台湾国防部周二表示，中国正在该地区海域部署近三十年来最大规模的海军舰队，对台湾构成的威胁比之前的中国军演更为明显。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 02:11:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-reports-surge-chinese-military-aircraft-ships-operating-nearby-2024-12-10/</guid></item><item><title>油价回落，但中国政策立场遏制损失</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/oil-prices-ease-geopolitical-risk-china-policy-stance-check-losses-2024-12-10/</link><description>由于对叙利亚总统巴沙尔·阿萨德被推翻的影响有所缓解，油价周二下跌，但市场发现中国承诺加大政策刺激力度，这可能会提振全球最大原油买家的需求。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 02:00:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/oil-prices-ease-geopolitical-risk-china-policy-stance-check-losses-2024-12-10/</guid></item><item><title>中国股市因政治局政策转变而上涨；澳洲联储之后澳元下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-12-10/</link><description>周二，中国股市飙升，大宗商品在北京新的降息和提振消费承诺的推动下获得支撑，而澳元下跌，全球股市在关键的美国通胀数据公布之前波动。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 01:59:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-12-10/</guid></item><item><title>台美首个贸易倡议协议生效</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/first-agreement-under-taiwan-us-trade-initiative-come-into-force-2024-12-10/</link><description>两国政府宣布，台湾和美国根据贸易倡议签署的第一份协议将于周二生效，台北希望正在进行的一系列谈判最终能达成自由贸易协议。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 00:46:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/first-agreement-under-taiwan-us-trade-initiative-come-into-force-2024-12-10/</guid></item><item><title>美国各机构将向众议院通报中国盐台风电信黑客攻击事件</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/us-agencies-brief-house-chinese-salt-typhoon-telecom-hacking-2024-12-09/</link><description>官员们周一表示，美国政府机构将于周二向众议院举行一次机密简报会，内容涉及中国所谓的“盐台风”渗透美国电信公司并窃取美国通话数据的行为。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 22:14:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/us-agencies-brief-house-chinese-salt-typhoon-telecom-hacking-2024-12-09/</guid></item></channel></rss>